'''潮热'''（英語：hot flash）多发于女性[[更年期|更年期]]时，因為體內的[[雌二醇|雌二醇]]減少而引起{{tsl|en|Flushing (physiology)|皮膚發紅}}的一种生理症狀。
導致潮熱的因素可能不只一種，然而常見的因素是：於[[更年期|更年期]]時，體內的[[荷爾蒙|荷爾蒙]]下降而引起。
遇到潮熱的人大多會感受到燥熱、多汗和心跳快速等，而且每次潮熱大概會持續2~30分鐘不等。

==症狀和體徵兆==
有潮熱症狀的人（常見於處在[[更年期|更年期]]和[[近更年期|近更年期]]<!--perimenopause-->的人）大多會感受到燥熱、[[汗液|多汗]]和[[心跳|心跳]]快速等。每次潮熱大概會持續2~30分鐘不等，潮熱結束時，症狀也會很快消失。

嚴重的潮熱可能導致晚上睡眠品質變差，進而引起[[失眠|失眠]]、影響[[心情|心情]]、[[專注力|專注力]]、和其他生理問題。

出現在深夜的潮熱也被稱為「夜裡盜汗（night sweats）」。這是因為[[雌激素|雌激素]]在體內的濃度通常在深夜時分最低。有些女性可能遇到夜裡盜汗，但其他時候卻無潮熱發生的狀況<ref>{{cite web | author = University of Glasgow | authorlink = University of Glasgow | title = Doctors seek the key to understanding hot flushes | work = University News (Archive of news) | publisher = University of Glasgow | date = 24 October 2007 | url = http://www.gla.ac.uk/news/archiveofnews/2007/october/headline_50212_en.html | accessdate = 19 April 2013 | archive-date = 2019-06-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190611164235/https://www.gla.ac.uk/news/archiveofnews/2007/october/headline_50212_en.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。
===年輕女性 ===
如果年輕女性遇到潮熱，則可能是[[腦下垂體|腦下垂體]]出問題的徵兆，應該盡速至神經科求診。
如果是手術關係導致提前停經，則潮熱的強度可能會高於自然停經的女性且持續到自然停經的年紀
<ref name="Menopause on About.com">{{cite web | last = About.com | title = Menopause | publisher = About.com | date = n.d. | url = http://adam.about.net/reports/Menopause.htm | accessdate = 19 April 2013 | archive-date = 2011-03-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110309173415/http://adam.about.net/reports/Menopause.htm | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。

===男性===
男性出現潮紅的原因可能有很多。潮紅對男性來說可能是低[[睪丸素|睪丸素]]的徵兆<ref>{{cite web | last = Bunyavanich | first = Supinda | title = Low Testosterone Could Kill You | work = ABC News | publisher = ABC News Internet Ventures | date = 6 June 2007 | url = http://abcnews.go.com/Health/ActiveAging/story?id=3247773#.UXKwlcWhhCI | accessdate = 20 April 2013 | archive-date = 2020-11-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201111194321/https://abcnews.go.com/Health/ActiveAging/story?id=3247773#.UXKwlcWhhCI | dead-url = no }}</ref>。 
另一個可能的徵兆則是：{{tsl|en|andropause|男性更年期}}<ref name="livestrong.com">{{cite web | last = Holley | first = Casey L. | title = 5 Things You Need to Know About the Causes of Hot Flashes in Men | work = Livestrong.com | publisher = Demand Media Inc. | date = 11 August 2011 | url = http://www.livestrong.com/article/9770-need-causes-hot-flashes-men/ | accessdate = 20 April 2013 | archive-date = 2019-06-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190630060641/https://www.livestrong.com/article/9770-need-causes-hot-flashes-men/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。 
罹患[[前列腺癌|前列腺癌]]或[[睾丸癌|睾丸癌]]的男性也可能遇到潮熱。在那些正在以[[抗雄激素|抗雄激素]]治療的人來說，潮熱出現的機率也會大增，因為這會讓睪丸素的濃度降到與睪丸被閹割後睪丸素水平附近<ref>{{cite web | title = What to Expect During Therapy | work = Lupron Depot | publisher = Abbott Laboratories | url = http://www.lupronadvancedprostatecancer.com/about-lupron-depot/what-to-expect-during-therapy.cfm | accessdate = 20 April 2013 | archive-date = 2013-11-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131123024938/http://www.lupronadvancedprostatecancer.com/about-lupron-depot/what-to-expect-during-therapy.cfm | dead-url = no }}</ref>。 
例如曾被[[閹割|閹割]]的人也較有可能遇到潮熱<ref>{{cite web | title = Hot Flashes In Men -- Mayo Clinic Researchers Describe A Treatment | work = ScienceDaily | publisher = Science Daily LLC | date = 19 October 2004 | url = http://sciencedaily.com/releases/2004/10/041019085808.htm | accessdate = 20 April 2013 | archive-date = 2021-03-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210309175802/http://www.sciencedaily.com/releases/2004/10/041019085808.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | last = Engstrom | first = Christine A. | last2 = Kasper | first2 = Christine E. | title = Physiology and Endocrinology of Hot Flashes in Prostate Cancer | journal = American Journal of Men's Health | volume = 1 | issue = 1 | pages = 8–17 | publisher = Sage Publications | date = March 2007 | url = http://jmh.sagepub.com/content/1/1/8.abstract | doi = 10.1177/1557988306294162 | accessdate = 20 April 2013 | archive-date = 2012-08-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120814074635/http://jmh.sagepub.com/content/1/1/8.abstract | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | last = Anitei | first = Stefan | title = Men Can Experience Hot Flashes, Just Like Women in Menopause | work = Softpedia | publisher = Softpedia | date = 16 April 2007 | url = http://news.softpedia.com/news/Men-Can-Experience-Hot-Flashes-Like-Menopause-Women-52030.shtml | accessdate = 20 April 2013 | archive-date = 2020-08-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200807183147/https://news.softpedia.com/news/Men-Can-Experience-Hot-Flashes-Like-Menopause-Women-52030.shtml | dead-url = no }}</ref>。
當然還有其他病症（ailment not aliment）可能導致男性潮紅。[[飲食|飲食]]也有可能在潮紅中扮演一個腳色<ref name="livestrong.com"/>。 

==中醫觀點==
部分品質不高的证据指出[[针灸|针灸]]可以緩解出現在[[乳癌|乳癌]]婦女或患有[[攝護腺癌|攝護腺癌]]（prostate cancer）男性的潮熱<ref>{{cite journal|last=Frisk|first=Jessica W.|author2=Hammar, Mats L.|author3=Ingvar, Martin|author4=Spetz Holm, Anna-Clara E.|title=How long do the effects of acupuncture on hot flashes persist in cancer patients?|journal={{tsl|en|Supportive Care in Cancer||Supportive Care in Cancer}}|date=30 January 2014|volume=22|issue=5|pages=1409–1415|doi=10.1007/s00520-014-2126-2|url=http://link.springer.com/article/10.1007%2Fs00520-014-2126-2|access-date=2017-07-16|archive-date=2019-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190629155034/https://link.springer.com/article/10.1007/s00520-014-2126-2|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|author1=MS Lee |author2=KH Kim |author3=BC Shin |author4=E Ernst |title=Acupuncture for treating hot flushes in men with prostate cancer: a systematic review|journal=Supportive Care in Cancer|date=July 2009|volume=17|issue=7|pages=763–70|pmid=19224253|doi=10.1007/s00520-009-0589-3}}</ref>。

